This paper deals with the problem of identifying similar content in order to suggest articles that have already been verified before. This task involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques, which are commonly used in the sub-fields of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the problem of identifying and classifying misinformation is also relevant to the sub-field of computer security (cs.CR). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories for this paper are cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.CR.
